    "name": "Titan Isles",
    "steam_appid": 1839680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >泰坦岛》是一款动作冒险游戏，要求玩家在压力下移动、随机应变并保持精准。掌握四种不同的外星战衣，升级自己的能力，打倒巨大的泰坦</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>四种玩法</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从四种独特的外星战衣中进行选择，每种战衣都有不同的移动方式、武器和能力。感觉就像在玩四款不同的游戏！在不同任务之间交换战衣，尝试新的移动和战斗方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/110b5a81e5bdce14401979ba606d2cf6.poster.avif?t=1769179431\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/110b5a81e5bdce14401979ba606d2cf6.webm?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/110b5a81e5bdce14401979ba606d2cf6.mp4?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>猎杀泰坦</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对主宰战场的巨大、影响世界的泰坦巨人。学会解读它们的攻击，保持机动性，并找到有创意的反击机会。击败每一个泰坦都会解锁强大的升级，并揭示他们觉醒背后的更多奥秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/cfc94d1844295d89779f4a6ad53b7f7d.poster.avif?t=1769179431\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/cfc94d1844295d89779f4a6ad53b7f7d.webm?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/cfc94d1844295d89779f4a6ad53b7f7d.mp4?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>单人或合作游戏</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在单人游戏或最多四人的合作游戏中，尽情展示您击杀泰坦的技能。任务、敌人和奖励会根据团队规模和协调性动态调整。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/02439934e33cdfdc23533ca9ea83fb79.poster.avif?t=1769179431\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/02439934e33cdfdc23533ca9ea83fb79.webm?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/02439934e33cdfdc23533ca9ea83fb79.mp4?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越支离破碎的世界</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越泰坦岛的漂浮废墟--从丛林树冠和熔岩洞穴到暴风肆虐的悬崖和冰冻山峰。每个生物群落都会带来新的穿越挑战，隐藏的奖励等待您去发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/3ca615982d1cd8d38e3db636e4e54612.poster.avif?t=1769179431\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/3ca615982d1cd8d38e3db636e4e54612.webm?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/3ca615982d1cd8d38e3db636e4e54612.mp4?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在竞技比赛中测试你的速度</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在赛车迷你游戏中测试您的外星战衣技能。与朋友和玩家一较高下，争夺排行榜第一名！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/2b85bfb9b9b3f7339431e02a526c4160.poster.avif?t=1769179431\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/2b85bfb9b9b3f7339431e02a526c4160.webm?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839680/extras/2b85bfb9b9b3f7339431e02a526c4160.mp4?t=1769179431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
